After the [[Evasive Action: End Game|fourth Evasive Action webstrip]], [[Tom Hodges]] and [[Karen Traviss]] were going to collaborate to create a '''new [[Star Wars comic books|webstrip]]''' for [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Star Wars Hyperspace]]. Hodges implied that it could involve [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorians]].

Hodges himself first announced this webstrip, however no official confirmation has come from [[Lucas Licensing]] yet. As of the beginning of [[2013]], there were no known plans to release this webstrip in the near future.

